三、教學目標 Objectives


1. 提昇音樂與人文藝術的素養2. 增進美的鑑賞能力與生活品味3. 培育豐富的想像力與創造力4. 培養具多元文化與國際觀 


1.To enhance the quality of music and the arts2.To promote the ability to appreciate beauty and lifestyle3.To cultivate a rich imagination and creativity4.To train with a multicultural and international perspective 


四、課程內容 Course Description


●整體敘述 Overall Description在音樂基礎理論與實用中，從音樂與文學、美術、戲劇等多元的文化面向中，結合古典、爵士與流行等不同議題，希望培育學生學習體認各種音樂藝術價值、風格及其文化脈絡，從藝術的陶冶中更豐富人文素養，進而喜愛參與藝文活動，期能增進「美」的創意能力。進而藉由世界觀的人文素養，以一位身心平衡的健康人為出發點，去服務他人與社會，追求人我、群己、天人和諧的藝術人生。In the overall curriculum of music theory and practice, this course aims to combine the different topics on classical music, jazz and today’s pop music from the literature, arts and drama in today’s world culture and to cultivate in students an appreciation of the value of musical art, style and cultural variety that is woven into our rich heritage in the arts and humanities. Thus encouragement in the participation to discover individually the "beauty" of creativity in the Arts and Humanities is stressed. It is hoped that through this course, a better world view emerges and will lead further to a balanced and healthy psycho- physical self in order to serve others in society. Only then does one’s pursuits in life either individually or as a group will come into harmony among our fellowmen.

